name: CTXMAMCompliance
summary: CTXMAMCompliance is responsible for ensuring that the device is compliant with the company policy.
description: CTXMAMCompliance is responsible for ensuring that the device is compliant with the company policy, for example checking if the device is configured with a passcode or if the device is jailbroken. See https://developer.cloud.com/citrixworkspace/mobile-application-integration to learn more.
